{
  "stem": "4963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And transports consisted of a group of about 30 people who usually went on a pickup truck, on a large truck, and-- covered truck, and they would go for about, I would say, an hour or two ride to-- to the border, to the woods.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we would have to walk through the woods.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean that's what-- how you-- how you went underground.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that's how I-- my experience, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's why I wanted to say how it consisted-- what it involved.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, many transports-- I wouldn't say many, but a number of transports were caught because you had to walk through the border, through the woods.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Russians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they immediately called in the upper-- the-- the higher officials, and they were taken into prisons and beaten and sent back into-- into prison camps, Russian labor camps.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And incidentally, my father-- well, while I was-- when I was liberated I found out later on that-- well, I didn't have-- I didn't know too much about my parents, but I suppose later on-- no, that-- in thinking back, it was really after in Germany later on I found out how my father died in a Russian concentration-- in a Russian labor camp.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyhow, let's proceed with the story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my aunt-- so Schmuel was-- so many-- some transports were caught and, you know, go-- got-- having to go back into labor camps and-- and prisons and so on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My aunt and uncle established themselves quite well in Kaunas, so Schmuel wanted to take them out, and my aunt felt that she really didn't want to go through this again.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
